I now understand "icon" refers to the Profile avatar button in the header of `HomeScreen.tsx`. I'm going to add the logout button adjacent to it, modifying the header section. I will likely need to adjust the flexbox layout to accommodate the new button. The code snippet shows the existing layout; now I'll modify it to include the logout function.


