I have removed the "Cerrar Sesión" button from the `EditProfileModal` component. Next, I plan to integrate the button below the profile icon on the `HomeScreen`. To do this, I will add it to the header section using a column-based layout. The next steps will involve transferring the `handleLogout` function and styling the button for consistency. I want to create a solution that is simple, intuitive, and consistent. I am now working on making the updated code.


**Integrating Logout Function**

I've completed the code changes and integrated the logout functionality. I've removed the button from `EditProfileModal` and added a new "Cerrar Sesión" button in the `HomeScreen` header, right below the profile button. The button uses the icon and styles I described. I used the existing imports for `signOut` and `auth` and moved `handleLogout` to `HomeScreen`. Everything should be working now, I have the final code here:
```typescript
import { signOut } from 'firebase/auth';
import { auth } from '../services/firebase';

const HomeScreen = () => {

// ... existing code

    const handleLogout = async () => {
        if (window.confirm("¿Desea cerrar sesión?")) {
            try {
                await signOut(auth);
                window.location.reload();
            } catch (error) {
                console.error("Logout failed", error);
                window.location.reload();
            }
        }
    };
    return (
        // ...Existing code

        <View className="flex flex-col bg-white h-full relative"  >
            <Header />
            <View className="p-4" >
                //... existing code
            </View>
        </View>
    );

    function Header() {
        return (
            <View className="flex flex-row items-center justify-between p-4 bg-gray-100">
                <View>
                    //... existing text
                </View>
                <View className="flex flex-col items-end">
                    <ProfileButton />
                    <TouchableOpacity
                        onPress={handleLogout}
                        className="flex flex-row items-center mt-2 px-3 py-1 rounded bg-red-200">
                        <Svg width={24} height={24} viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M17 16L21 12M21 12L17 8M21 12H7M13 16V17C13 19.2091 11.2091 21 9 21H6C3.79086 21 2 19.2091 2 17V7C2 4.79086 3.79086 3 6 3H9C11.2091 3 13 4.79086 13 7V8" stroke="#000000" strokeWidth="2" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" />
                        </Svg>
                        <Text className="text-sm ml-2">Cerrar Sesión</Text>
                    </TouchableOpacity>
                </View>
            </View>
        );
    }
};

export default HomeScreen;
```
